	"name": "Lesson 3",
	"text": [
		"<p>Lesson 3 - Introducing Errors</p>",
		"<p>Let's get started....</p>",
		"<p>In the console, type: </p>",
		"<p class='codeText'>",
		"cd ~/work</br>",
		"mkdir Errors</br>",
		"cd Errors</p>",
		"<p>Now we have our working directory. Now , lets create our code file: </p>",
		"<p class='codeText'>vim main.go</p>",
		"<p>Type i to begin editing the file. Now, type the following:</p>",
		"<p  class='codeText'>",
		"package main</br>",
		"</br>",
		"import (</br>",
		"        'fmt'</br>",
		")</br>",
		"</br>",
		"func addition(x int, y int)int {</br>",
		"        return x + y</br>",
		"}</br>",
		"</br>",
		"func main() { </br>",
		"var s string = 'three'</br>",
		"fmt.Println(addition(1,2))</br>",
		"}</p>",
		"<p>Now save the file by hitting ESC key typing: :wq!</p>",
		"<p>Now you can run your program by typing:</p>",
		"<p  class='codeText'>",
		"go run main.go</p>",
		"<p>You should see an error complaining about string and int.</p>",
		"<p>To fix this, change the following:</p>",
		"<p class='codeText'>var s string = 'three'</p>",
		"<p>to</p>",
		"<p class='codeText'>var s int = 3</p>",
		"<p>Save and rerun your code.</p>",
		"<p style='color:green;'>Congratulations! You have started troubleshooting!</p>"
		]
}
